    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "You get an empty array because `referrals[msg.sender]` (in `getReferrals`) and `referrals[referrer]` (in `becomeReferral`) are only the same array if `msg.sender` and `referrer` hold the same value.\r\n\r\nClosing this because it is neither a bug nor a feature request. If you have further questions, please either ask in https://gitter.im/ethereum/solidity or https://ethereum.stackexchange.com/",
